data.description: If you are looking for historical charm, look no further!  This home maintains some of it's past elegance with a grand front staircase, stunning wallpapers, hardwood floors, and stained glass.  There is plenty of room with three bedrooms, two full baths, and a bonus room.  There is an attic, partial basement, and detached two car garage for extra storage. A wheelchair ramp and a walk-in shower give this old house some accessibility.  Come relax on the covered front porch on your own corner lot! House is being sold As Is.
